---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Cookies" showLegal={false}>
  <div
    class="max-w-[400px] mx-auto bg-white p-5 rounded-sm flex flex-col gap-3"
  >
    <p class="font-bold text-xl mb-6 mt-2">Cookie Policy</p>

    <p class="text-sm">
      This website uses cookies to improve the user experience and analyze how
      the website is used. Below we explain what cookies are, which types we use
      and how you can manage them.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-medium">1. What are cookies?</h2>

    <p class="text-sm">
      Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you visit
      a website. They allow information about your visit to be remembered in
      order to facilitate navigation and improve the user experience.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-medium">2. Types of cookies used</h2>

    <p class="text-sm">
      This website uses the following categories of cookies. Analytical cookies
      will only be installed if the user gives their consent.
    </p>

    <ul class="text-sm list-disc pl-5">
      <li>
        <b>Technical cookies:</b> necessary for the basic functioning of the website.
      </li>

      <li>
        <b>Analytical cookies:</b> allow us to analyze user behavior on the website
        in order to improve our services.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-medium">3. Third-party cookies</h2>

    <p class="text-sm">
      This website may use third-party services that install cookies on your
      device for analytical purposes. In particular, analysis tools provided by
      Google through Google Tag Manager are used to obtain statistics about the
      use of the website.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-medium">4. Cookie management</h2>

    <p class="text-sm">
      When accessing this website, a banner will be displayed allowing you to
      accept or reject the use of analytical cookies.
    </p>

    <p class="text-sm">
      You can also configure your browser to block or delete cookies installed
      on your device.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-medium">5. More information</h2>

    <p class="text-sm">
      For more information about how your personal data is processed, please
      consult our <a href="/en/privacy" class="underline text-blue-600">
        Privacy Policy
      </a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
